    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add your<strong> white</strong> <strong>miso paste</strong> and <strong>mirin</strong> to a small bowl with 1 tbsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[1 1/2 tbsp]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[2 tbsp]</span> <strong>vegetable oil</strong>, season with <strong>salt </strong>and <strong>pepper</strong> and give everything a good mix up<strong> </strong>– this is your<strong> miso glaze</strong></p><p>Peel (scrape the skin off with a teaspoon) and finely chop your <strong>ginger</strong> into matchsticks</p><p>Peel and finely slice (don't chop!) your<strong> garlic</strong></p>",
