    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, heat a separate, large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) with a drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil</strong> over a medium-high heat</p><p>Once hot, add the<strong> sliced spring greens</strong> and <strong>chopped</strong> <strong>pak choi base </strong>and cook for 2-3 min or until starting to wilt</p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
