    {
      "instruction": "<p>Drain the <strong>refreshed edamame beans</strong>, then add them to the pan with the <strong>pak choi tops</strong>, <strong>ginger matchsticks</strong> and <strong>sliced garlic</strong> and cook for a further 2-3 min or until fragrant and everything is tender with a bite</p><p>Add your <strong>soy sauce</strong> and give everything a good mix up – these are your<strong> stir-fried ginger greens</strong></p>",
