    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the tofu has browned, add the <strong>miso glaze </strong>and cook for 2-3 min or until the sauce has coated the tofu and is starting to caramelise</p><p>Sprinkle over your <strong>black sesame seeds </strong>– this is your <strong>miso tofu</strong></p>",
